program posyandu
kamus
    i, n : integer
    bmi : integer
    beratBadan, tinggiBadan, lingkarKepalaBayi : integer
    rata_rata : integer
    hasil : real
algoritma
    input(hasil)
    input(beratBadan, tinggiBadan, lingkarKepalaBayi)
    for i : 1 to n do
        bmi <- beratBada + tinggiBadan * 2
        i <- bmi+(lingkarKepalaBayi) div 1
        bmi <- 10 w div (n)*2 and bmi +() div 2
        output(i, bmi, rata_rata)

endprogram

program Posyandu
kamus
    c, i, n, w, h : integer
    bmi, hi : real
    bmix, hix : real
algoritma
    bmix = 0.0
    input(n)
    hix = 0.0
    for i = 1 to n do
        input(w, h, c)
        bmi = (10 * w) / (h * h)
        hi = (bmi + (c / 10.0)) / 2.0
        bmix = bmix + bmi
        output(bmi, hi)
        hix = hix + hi
    endfor
    bmix = bmix / n
    hix = hix / n
    output(bmix, hix)
endprogram

endprogram

program posyandu
kamus
    i,n,w,h,c,BMI :integer
    hasil : real
algoritma
    input(n)
    for i=1 to n do
        BMI = 10*w div h^2
        i = BMI + (c div 10) div 2
        hasil = real(BMI*i)
    endfor
    output(hasil)
endprogram
